net.hudup.core.evaluate

Class EvaluatorConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.data.PropList
      • net.hudup.core.data.DataConfig
        • net.hudup.core.data.SysConfig
          • net.hudup.core.evaluate.EvaluatorConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, TextParsable

    public class EvaluatorConfig
extends SysConfig
    This class specifies the configuration of an evaluator represented (Evaluator. Recall that Evaluator is one of main classes of Hudup framework, which is responsible for executing and evaluation algorithms according to built-in and user-defined metrics.

    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
